{{italic title}} '''''Sabdatharavali''''' (A star cluster of words) is a [[Malayalam]] [[dictionary]] having more than 1800 pages and considered as the most authentic Malayalam dictionary of the 20th century. The first part of this dictionary authored by [[Sreekanteswaram Padmanabha Pillai]] was published in 1918.
